List all datasets

Source: R/ods_all_datasets.R
ods_all_datasets.Rd

ods_all_datasets returns details of all datasets available from statistics.gov.scot

ods_all_datasets()

Value

data.frame. Contains the URI, Name, Publisher and Dataset Name of every dataset.

Examples

ods_all_datasets()
